Localization.Name: OMNI-CFS-Diamond Flight Suit
Localization.ShortName:
Item Type: Flight Suit
Damage Reduction: 10%
Temp. Rating: -30 / 60 °C
Radiation Protection: 15200 REM
Radiation Scrub Rate: 81 REM/s
Carrying Capacity: 8.0 µSCU

The Navy has spent centuries refining the flight suits that their combat pilots wear. The OMNI-CFS Diamond is the culmination of this long and battle-tested military. The Omni features reinforced construction to withstand a variety of hostile environments and integrates flawlessly with appropriately classic armor systems.
